    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关羽",
        "四军士",
        "报子",
        "旗牌"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四月华旗手、四马童、大马童、关羽同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秉丹心，扫荡烟尘，扶汉室，扭转乾坤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桃园结拜义同心，纵横天下显奇能。赤胆忠心冲宇宙，扫尽狼烟灭奸臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，汉室关。弟兄结义以来，久战疆场，威名远振。某大哥镇守徐州，三弟统\n兵小沛，某奉大哥重托，保定二嫂，镇守下邳。可恨曹操，上欺天子，下压群\n臣。闻得曹操带兵攻打徐州，不知大哥胜负如何，也曾命人前去哨探，未见回\n报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀二将军：徐州已破，刘使君不知下落，有徐州兵丁，逃到此间，辕门哭告，\n要求二将军收留，现在辕门候令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是徐州逃来的军兵，不可欺压他们，唤他们进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐州兵丁进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四军士同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四军士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与二将军叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操攻破徐州，使君何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四军士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘使君不知下落。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四军士同哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汝等不必悲痛，各自休息几日，随营报效。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四军士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢二将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四军士同下。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀二将军：徐州已破，小沛已失，使君与三将军不知下落。曹操统领人马，\n攻打下邳，特来报知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，探马报道，曹兵夺了徐州，大哥、三弟不知下落……也罢！俺不免出城\n与曹军决一死战。\n众将官，开城迎敌去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人出城同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "旗牌→关羽",
          "turns": 1
