    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关羽",
        "张辽"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四上手、曹将、夏侯惇同上，过场，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四月华旗手、四马童、大马童、关羽同上，站门，会阵开打，夏侯惇败下，关羽、四月华旗手、四马童、"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大马童同追下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四文堂、郭嘉、程昱、荀彧、荀攸同上。四军士同上，出城迎曹操同进城，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四大刀手、乐进、路昭、朱灵、于禁、夏侯渊同上。曹将、夏侯惇同上。关羽、四月华旗手、四"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马童、大马童同上，会阵开打，曹将败下。关羽破大刀手，追下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四上手、张郃、宋宪、徐晃、许褚同上。曹将同上。关羽、四月华旗手、四马童、大马童同上，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "会阵，上山。曹将双抄，两边下。起火。关羽站山头。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "四面俱是曹兵将，\n眼望下邳火光亮——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只见关羽困山岗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云长公，别来无恙？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文远，欲来相敌耶？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非也。念故人旧日之情，特来相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，请下马上山叙谈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟下马上山来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽上山，关羽、张辽分坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文远莫非说关某汉乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不然。昔日蒙兄救弟，弟今日安得不来救兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "然则文远将欲助我乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦非也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既不助我，此来何干？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玄德不知存亡，翼德未知生死。昨日曹公已破下邳，军民毫无伤损，并差人护\n玄德家眷，不许惊扰。如此相待，弟特来报兄，免得悬挂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯……我今虽处绝地，视死如归。汝当速去，吾即下山迎战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……兄出此言，岂不被天下人耻笑乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我为忠义而死，安得为天下人耻笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄今若死，其罪有三。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汝且说我哪三罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关兄听道：当初刘使君与兄结义之时，誓同生死，今使君方败，而兄战死，倘\n使君复出，欲求兄相助，而不可得，岂不负当年之盟誓？其罪一也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问二罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘使君以家眷付托与兄，兄今战死，二位夫人无所依赖，负却使君付托之重，\n其罪二也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问这三罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄武艺超群，兼通经史，不思与使君匡扶汉室徒欲赴汤蹈火，以逞匹夫之勇，\n安得为义，其罪三也！兄有此三罪，弟不得不告，望兄详细思之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汝说我有三罪，欲我如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今四面皆曹公之兵，兄若不降，则必战死，徒死无益，不如且降曹公，打听刘\n使君下落，即往投之，一者可以保二夫人，二者不背桃园之约，三者可留有用\n之身，以图后举。有此三便，望兄再思再想。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄言三便，吾有三约。如丞相能从我，当即卸甲，如其不允，吾宁受三罪而死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相宽宏大量，何所不容，愿闻一事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一者，吾与皇叔，誓扶汉室，吾今只降汉帝，不降曹操。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问二事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二者，二位嫂嫂要食某大哥之俸禄，一应上下人等皆不许擅入内室。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问三事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三者，但知刘皇叔去向，不管千里万里，便当辞去。三者缺一，断不肯降，望\n文远急急回报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这三事重大，待俺秉知丞相再议。请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽下山，上马，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二幕下。关羽下。众人随下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
