      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽上，下马，上山。二幕启。关羽在山上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关兄三事，丞相无一不从。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然如此，暂请丞相退军，容我入城见过二嫂，告知其事，然后再行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何难。\n嘚，众将官！丞相有令，将人马退后十里，各归队伍。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹将自两边同抄下。关羽、张辽同下山，上马，进城，同下。）"
        }
      ],
